                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="registrationFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="collapseFour" data-parent="#Registration">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>Choose from the updated slots listed on the website. Want to register for more than one slot at a
                    time? Get in touch: syed@oxfamindia.org / 8884088821</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                  <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                          data-target="#registrationFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="registrationFive">
                    5. Can I change my event format/ slot after registration?
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="registrationFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="registrationFive"
                   data-parent="#Registration">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>No, once you register, you cannot change the slot or format.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                  <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                          data-target="#registrationSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="registrationSix">
                    6. Is there an age limit to participate in the event?
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="registrationSix" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="registrationSix" data-parent="#Registration">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>No age limit — anyone, absolutely anyone, who has passion for fitness and resonates with Oxfam
                    India’s work, can participate!</p>

                  <p>In case you are 60+, we advise you to consult a medical expert given the nature of event.
                    For minors participating in the challenge, we strongly advise adult/parental supervision.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
