                    1. I forgot my login password, what should I do?
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>

              <div id="postOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#Post">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>Click on the 'forgot password' option to receive a password resent link on your registered email
