                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                  <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                          data-target="#postTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="postTwo">
                    2. I logged in but can’t locate my dashboard. Why?
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="postTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#Post">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>Your dashboard is activated on Day 1 of your chosen challenge slot. You will not be able to access
                    it before that. </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                  <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                          data-target="#postThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="postThree">
                    3. How do I submit my activity?
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="postThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#Post">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>After registering successfully, upload activity on your personal dashboard.</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Log in to your account</li>
                    <li>You will reach the dashboard</li>
                    <li>Here, enter the kilometres walked</li>
                    <li>Upload the screenshot (one screenshot per day)</li>
                    <li>Submit Activity</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                  <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                          data-target="#postFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="postFour">
                    4. What mobile apps shall I use for submitting proof of my activity?
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="postFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="postFour" data-parent="#Post">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>Screenshots from all major fitness applications are acceptable. Some recommendations – ADIDAS
                    RUNNING, APPLE WATCH, FITBIT, GARMIN CONNECT, GOOGLE FIT, NIKE RUN CLUB, PUMATRAC, STRAVA,
                    RUNKEEPER, MAP MY WALK and MAP MY RUN by UNDER ARMOUR, or others.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                  <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                          data-target="#postFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="postFive">
                    5. Where can I check my total distance walked, and distance left to complet5
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="postFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="postFive" data-parent="#Post">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>You will receive a progress email on your registered email ID every time you update your activity/
                    progress data on the dashboard.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                  <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                          data-target="#postSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="postSix">
                    6. Why I am not receiving any emails?
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="postSix" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="postSix" data-parent="#Post">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>Please check your spam/ junk folders. If you still don’t locate emails, get in touch with us.</p>


                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

