                  <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                          data-target="#postSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="postSeven">
                    7. Can I upload the activity data for multiple days in one go?
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="postSeven" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="postSeven" data-parent="#Post">
