                <div class="card-body">
                  <p>There are multiple ways one can cheat during a virtual challenge. But when they do,
                    they cheat themselves more than the organisers or other participants. The Virtual Oxfam Trailwalker
                    is a non-competitive event, everyone is a winner.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
