                    2. Do I receive 80G certificate/Tax exemption
                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down pull-right"></i>
                  </button>
                </h2>
              </div>
              <div id="donationTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#Donation">
